prompts.frontCover: A humorous watercolor painting of a cartoon-style slice of cherry pie with big googly eyes, looking panicked and running away on two little crust legs. A single cartoon fork with a mischievous grin is chasing it. Soft, flowing watercolor style with artistic splatters and organic paint bleeds on a textured paper background. Centered in the middle, the text "happy birthday" is written in a beautiful, readable, flowing handwritten cursive script. Flat 2D artwork.
